Name: Average time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time elapsed for all instances of 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time difference between 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' for manuscripts that undergo both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission and activity SW-Reviewer Agreed for cases where activity SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Total time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total duration of all 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' activities before 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes from 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
